Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, my name is not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought to my hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer! Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner! It's me, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought Anna…\NI mean, I brought Nina home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll call the police from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like the police came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The cigarettes you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I… killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-I killed him.\N-Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago, I killed my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I was the one\Nwho brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police, and we're here\Nto respond to a call from this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check out the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you both alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Backup will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We will let them secure the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask you two some questions\Nat the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the victims' daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you did not see the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe something like this\Nwould happen in this peaceful town…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? China?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am Japanese. My name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You got yourself into big trouble\Nin a foreign land, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. We're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought the Heidelberg\NPolice Station was in the town center.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We are from the Mannheim Police Station\Nin the neighboring town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they taking us to the station\Nin the neighboring town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be there in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Responding to a call…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they say they got a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But… Who called the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line was cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't turn on the police siren\Nwhen they came either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't secure the scene right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they take away\Nthe first people to discover the bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However, their police ID looked real…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they the ones who…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A roadblock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for a hit-and-run suspect.\NPlease cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Detective Messener\Nand Detective Müller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is this a new car? It's nice!\N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get old very soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go out for some fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did those two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they actually detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that blood, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who called them?\NAnd they didn't use the siren…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? What should I…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay? Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you my name,\Nbut I never said I was a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a shop close by.\NI got you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's bread and some sausage and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I also asked them to put\Nsome hot coffee in the flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably aren't hungry,\Nbut you have to eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're chilled to the bone,\Nso you should change now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked with my brother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like we were the only two people\Nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it? Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We crossed the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The older couple encouraged us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so nice to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother told me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that he had a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the old couple died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people who were nice to us…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, I finally knew why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That rainy day…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the murder of the Lieberts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also the one who killed\Nall those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and aimed it at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my brother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed and told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "after you shoot me,\Nthrow the gun out of the window."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to aim for the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I aimed at his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had never saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad wouldn't have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If the detectives last night\Nwere actually police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it means someone in the police is\Nconnected to Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we can't stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Nina.\NJohan wants to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone comes, you have to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat something and drink some hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,People need to do that to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any clue to finding the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,HEIDELBERG POLICE STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this connected to the middle-aged\Ncouple serial murders across Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are doing everything we can\Nto solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we cannot divulge\Nany more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our information,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the Fortners had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's under investigation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reporter, Mr. Maurer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was he in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that Japanese man\Nwho was with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese? That's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the murder at Heidelberg Castle\Nthat happened at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the work of the same perpetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Heidelberg Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was killed, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We will release more information\Nwhen we are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Please let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you for coming\Nall the way from Mannheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Much appreciated,\NDetective Messener and Detective Müller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too kind. Please let us know\Nif there's anything we can help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the investigation going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in to talk more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They were actual police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They were detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chaos here\Nin the editorial department!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get the Japanese guy who was with Maurer.\N-What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, be quiet! I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there at five\Nwith an important witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not contact the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Is it another fake tip?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If the police can't be trusted,\Nwe can only go to the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only way to keep Nina safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just come in here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, as a BKA agent, aren't you here\Nfor the middle-aged couple murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only investigating the murder\Nat Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry about that. I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder you're investigating happened\Nat the same time with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't be the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's wrist has rope marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find any rope close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When we found the victim,\Nhe wasn't tied up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only four\Npossible escape routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The route has to be covert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The hiding place must have\Nfew people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! It's me. It's Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you don't have to hide now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he take Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma, this is not your fault."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"You only did\Nwhat you're supposed to do as a doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"You didn't do anything wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please have the sandwich."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Then try to get some sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"You have to stay alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please save as many people as you can."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nina Fortner."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to kill him once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I who brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved that monster…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought him back to life.
